{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"f7e65bd673","title":"毛主席接见伊朗左派革命组织代表团谈话记录","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"411f345130","index":0,"year":1970,"month":10,"day":1,"articleId":"f7e65bd673"}],"tags":[{"id":"314ad57c4d","name":"对话","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"44b4a39710","name":"林彪","type":"人物"},{"id":"523bb79e8f","name":"周恩来","type":"人物"},{"id":"57eea82497","name":"康生","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"44aa5fb3b9","type":"title","text":"毛主席接见伊朗左派革命组织代表团谈话记录","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"a5b68cef96","type":"paragraph","text":"时  间：1970年10月1日晚10时15分","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"792edb4065","type":"paragraph","text":"地  点：天安门城楼","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"f31c91976d","type":"paragraph","text":"参加人：伊方—雷兹瓦尼、哈桑、穆哈森","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"b6ee316b06","type":"paragraph","text":"中方—林彪、周恩来、康生","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"4fdf992722","type":"paragraph","text":"翻  译：伍书湖","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"55fdbe52a0","type":"paragraph","text":"（10月1日晚焰火结束后，周恩来总理把代表团引见给毛主席。周总理对毛主席说：“他们是伊朗同志。”毛主席迎上几步同他们亲切地握手。）","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"585b59fdf7","type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席（以下简称主席）：伊朗就是波斯，欢迎。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"76d7b7460d","type":"paragraph","text":"雷兹瓦尼（以下简称雷）：（用中文高呼）“毛主席万岁”。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"2061c781d5","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（同他们一一握手）谢谢同志们。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"2f99133833","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：见到毛主席是对我们最大的鼓舞。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"0642814592","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：（问康生）他们来多久了？","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"9bf6529dc5","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：一个多月了。","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"325cc0f6ff","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：你们愿意呆多久就呆多久。","index":13,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"583c99336e","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷用中文高呼“毛主席万岁！”）","index":14,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"b25b16108d","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：同志们万岁！同志们好，欢迎你们。","index":15,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"2789b4baee","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：能见到您，对我们是最大的鼓舞，我们一定努力做您的好学生。","index":16,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"609687fdb2","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：我们都是同志，我们向你们学习。","index":17,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"2596a9401d","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：毛主席万岁！","index":18,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"e86b02e052","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：谢谢。你们很年轻，未来是属于你们的。我老了，不行了。","index":19,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"e99ffcf29b","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷等人笑着摇头，用中文高呼“毛主席万岁！”）","index":20,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"f9f01e0651","type":"paragraph","text":"主席：祝你们革命胜利！","index":21,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"22897c356d","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷用中文高呼“毛主席万岁！”毛主席再次同代表团二同志一一握手告别，并向前走了几步微笑着挥手欢送他们。然后，周恩来总理把他们带到林彪面前，林从座位上站起来同他们握手。）","index":22,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"b17331f161","type":"paragraph","text":"林：欢迎你们！","index":23,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"e790efa7b0","type":"paragraph","text":"雷：我们看到毛主席和您，是对我们最大的鼓舞，我们一定要按照毛主席的指示办事。","index":24,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"5d37e71e7e","type":"paragraph","text":"林：你们会逐渐取得革命胜利的。","index":25,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"},{"id":"99114877b4","type":"paragraph","text":"（雷等同林握手告别，又同周总理握手告别，周总理用英文向他们说“再见”）","index":26,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673"}],"page":{"id":"2b05befe35","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"f7e65bd673","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}